### Comment APIs

# GET all comments
GET http://localhost:8000/comments

###

# GET comments of a specific post by title (slug)
GET http://localhost:8000/comments/양자-컴퓨팅의-혁명적-발전

###

# Create a new comment
POST http://localhost:8000/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "이것은 댓글입니다.",
  "userId": "6ba7b812-9dad-11d1-80b4-00c04fd430c8",
  "postId": 1
}

###

# Update a specific comment by ID
PATCH http://localhost:8000/comments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "수정된 댓글 내용입니다."
}

###

# Delete a specific comment by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8000/comments/1
